rows.label: tlk44100184_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Outlanders! Hey listen, apparently
when I'm older I'll be allowed to
leave Luxuria too!

rows.label: tlk44100184_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I really love plants. I read all about
them in an encyclopedia in the library.
I want to go out and find them all!

rows.label: tlk44100184_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But in the meantime, I need to go and
explore Luxuria and find all the plants
that haven't been discovered yet!
